keyFacts: An email notification shows Annie Phifer invited someone to collaborate on a Box folder titled 'Maxwell Amazon Records'.
The notification was sent via the official USAfx File Exchange system on September 15, 2021.
The folder name 'Maxwell Amazon Records' suggests it contains records related to Ghislaine Maxwell, potentially from Amazon.
The use of an official government file exchange system (USAfx) indicates this is part of official case-related document sharing.
The document is a system-generated notification, not the actual content of the shared files.
